 socialismo vallesano; a tale titolo fu certamente uno dei politici contemporanei pi\u00f9 in vista del cant."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q18628047", "itemLabel": "Karl Dellberg", "dhsid": "004986", "namefr": "", "articlefr": "", "namede": "Karl Dellberg", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karl_Dellberg", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "128406976"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q18628047", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "D", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/004986/2005-08-22"}